tags.description: Unincorporated community, unofficially called "Little Utah" because of historic association with the Satilla/Axson Branch of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, known locally as "Utah Church," whose meetinghouse stood nearby until 1979.
tags.name: Little Utah
tags.note: More information and resources about Little Utah, the old Utah Church and Cemetery, and the Latter-day Saints in the upper Satilla River basin can be found at the Satilla River Saints Project website: https://www.SatillaRiverSaints.org/LittleUtah.
